title: (Thurs Early Bird) Which Headline from Amy’s Life Is Fake? Game + Lunchbox Forgot A Major Milestone in His Life + Elder vs. Millennial
itunes:title: (Thurs Early Bird) Which Headline from Amy’s Life Is Fake? Game + Lunchbox Forgot A Major Milestone in His Life + Elder vs. Millennial
description:
Amy shares with us 3 headlines from her life that all sound crazy. We must guess which one is actually true. Lunchbox reveals that he forgot a major milestone in his life and wasn’t aware until his father-in-law texted him. Eddie and Morgan face off in Elder vs. Millennial.
